cmdGA

Class Match

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmdGA.Match

  • public class Match
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a match between a String and an Option object. Contains information the site of the match in the String (position and ending) and the option of reference.
    Author:
    Javier Iserte
